Changing that to ApplicationUser is super simple.

4
00:00:10,890 --> 00:00:14,430
But before I walk you through that, let me go back here,

5
00:00:14,430 --> 00:00:18,630
in area, identity, pages, account,

6
00:00:18,630 --> 00:00:20,310
we have register.

7
00:00:20,310 --> 00:00:23,550
Let me open the register page model.

8
00:00:23,550 --> 00:00:25,890
Again, this is a razor page here

9
00:00:25,890 --> 00:00:28,740
