38
00:01:49,830 --> 00:01:52,530
All we have to do is directly inject them

39
00:01:52,530 --> 00:01:54,480
in dependency injection

40
00:01:54,480 --> 00:01:58,620
and then using UserManager or SignInManager,

41
00:01:58,620 --> 00:02:00,363
