47
00:02:14,730 --> 00:02:17,343
with the help of these helper classes.

48
00:02:18,390 --> 00:02:19,530
If we scroll down,

49
00:02:19,530 --> 00:02:22,050
in razor pages if you remember,

50
00:02:22,050 --> 00:02:24,120
